{"tid":2222504,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［JJ插地］ 買左新ssd 裝完window  但入唔到window","createTime":"2020-09-29T06:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T15:05:32.000Z","uid":40348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c79f89a565c17d65d8248a34baa9401b9e2ddc5a","tid":2222504,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n本來有一隻250 gb ssd + 512 gb ssd + 1tb hdd<br />\n<br />\n咁250果隻裝完window 已經無乜位<br />\n所以買左隻1tb 既 ssd去換隻250 gb ssd<br />\n<br />\n咁我換果陣就直接將250gb既ssd d sata 線 <br />\n轉插去1tb ssd <br />\n<br />\n咁之後改開機順序啦<br />\n改完新ssd做第一順序 <br />\n再裝window <br />\n之後都好順利<br />\n<br />\n裝完window ，咁我就試下重新開機啦<br />\n重新開機就見到reboot and select proper boot device<br />\n<br />\n咁我直接禁f11 簡裝左隻新ssd 之後又會入到window<br />\n<br />\n入到去搵「我的電腦」果陣又搵唔到其他個兩隻hdd 同ssd <br />\n<br />\n而家問題有兩個<br />\n1. 點解開機佢直接入唔到去window <br />\n但係咁f 11撳咗隻新ssd 又會入到<br />\n2.入到新嗰隻Ssd之後點解會見唔到其他個兩隻hdd/ssd <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該晒咁多位巴打"},{"pid":"082aa7d520cefe118806bbf3710dffc2837bf873","tid":2222504,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"你3個device 分別咩介面架<br />\npcie 會同某啲sata頭唔可以一齊用<br />\n<br />\n同埋裝windows 最好拔晒其他hdd ssd, 佢個boot loader會認晒所有插住嘅 storage,裝完先插返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2053c6c8c30ae70d4726fdffeeab7f0bbf4479a0","tid":2222504,"uid":363468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"1. 係 BIOS 要 set 番 boot 機果隻 SSD<br />\n2. 其他果兩隻 HDD/SDD set 左 offline?"},{"pid":"82aee292ca856c739206af8b6b3ab46de778ce8b","tid":2222504,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"九成BIOS set錯嘢<br />\n但係你又講唔到BIOS settings<br />\n不如reset BIOS 等佢自己認"},{"pid":"893b24dc7ba524ef9363d44ebc1dd41acfb43779","tid":2222504,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"唔該晒三位大哥。我返去影一影bios 比你地睇🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"c6a2bc4711cd20f630b836bd89aef6987c042822","tid":2222504,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893b24dc7ba524ef9363d44ebc1dd41acfb43779","tid":2222504,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"唔該晒三位大哥。我返去影一影bios 比你地睇🙏🏻🙏🏻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"你貼個spec先啦"},{"pid":"8bd86f4a46294ef4a295d5c26ed52aa3d9e19969","tid":2222504,"uid":223305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z-i_-lQ2TPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz-i_-lQ2TPo&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=8f221ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z-i_-lQ2TPo</a><br />\n你跟著上面條片試完，再係「我的電腦」睇下見唔見到ssd 同 hdd"},{"pid":"d6dab0fba2d8eaa4c755fc6c12f283e505f89ff4","tid":2222504,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bd86f4a46294ef4a295d5c26ed52aa3d9e19969","tid":2222504,"uid":223305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z-i_-lQ2TPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz-i_-lQ2TPo&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=8f221ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z-i_-lQ2TPo</a><br />\n你跟著上面條片試完，再係「我的電腦」睇下見唔見到ssd 同 hdd"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔該晒🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"fa